<div class="modal-backdrop" id="settings-modal" aria-hidden="true">
  <section class="modal settings-modal" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="settings-title">
    <button class="modal-close" data-close="settings-modal">×</button>
    <h2 id="settings-title">Progression & paramètres</h2>
    <div class="dlc-settings">
      <span class="settings-label">CONTENU</span>
      <div class="dlc-current">
        <div><strong id="dlc-current-name">Infra Clicker</strong><small id="dlc-current-description">Construisez une infrastructure mondiale.</small></div>
        <select id="dlc-select" aria-label="Choisir un DLC"></select>
      </div>
      <small>Chaque DLC possède une progression locale indépendante. Les futurs DLC apparaîtront ici.</small>
    </div>
    <div class="theme-settings">
      <span class="settings-label">THÈME</span>
      <div class="theme-picker" id="theme-picker">
        <button class="theme-option" data-theme="ruby" title="Rouge rubis">
          <i style="--swatch:#f2a0aa"></i><span>Rubis</span>
        </button>
        <button class="theme-option" data-theme="sunset" title="Jaune et orange">
          <i style="--swatch:#f5c98b"></i><span>Sunset</span>
        </button>
        <button class="theme-option" data-theme="lavender" title="Violet lavande">
          <i style="--swatch:#c7b5ed"></i><span>Lavande</span>
        </button>
        <button class="theme-option" data-theme="mint" title="Vert menthe">
          <i style="--swatch:#9ed8bd"></i><span>Menthe</span>
        </button>
        <button class="theme-option active" data-theme="ocean" title="Bleu océan">
          <i style="--swatch:#9ccce8"></i><span>Océan</span>
        </button>
      </div>
      <small class="theme-hint">Ynov, Linear et NOC sont désormais des DLC (sélecteur ci-dessus).</small>
    </div>
    <div class="settings-actions">
      <button id="save-now" class="primary-button">Synchroniser avec le serveur</button>
      <button id="reset-game" class="danger-button">Réinitialiser la progression serveur</button>
      <button id="delete-local-data" class="secondary-button">Réinitialiser les préférences locales</button>
      <a href="/privacy" class="secondary-button privacy-link">Confidentialité et stockage</a>
    </div>
    <div class="save-status"><span class="status-dot"></span><span id="save-status">Synchronisé</span></div>
    <div class="security-status"><span>↻</span><div><strong>Synchronisation serveur active</strong><small>Progression locale envoyée automatiquement toutes les 5 secondes</small></div></div>
  </section>
</div>

<div class="modal-backdrop" id="achievements-modal" aria-hidden="true">
  <section class="modal achievements-modal" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="achievements-title">
    <button class="modal-close" data-close="achievements-modal">×</button>
    <h2 id="achievements-title">Succès</h2>
    <div id="achievement-grid" class="achievement-grid"></div>
  </section>
</div>

<div class="modal-backdrop" id="upgrades-modal" aria-hidden="true">
  <section class="modal game-menu-modal" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="upgrades-title">
    <button class="modal-close" data-close="upgrades-modal">×</button>
    <div class="modal-heading">
      <span class="modal-heading-icon upgrades-color">⬡</span>
      <div><h2 id="upgrades-title">Améliorations</h2><p>Choisissez une spécialité.</p></div>
    </div>
    <div class="upgrade-filters" id="upgrade-filters"></div>
    <div id="upgrade-grid" class="upgrade-grid"></div>
  </section>
</div>

<div class="modal-backdrop" id="certifications-modal" aria-hidden="true">
  <section class="modal game-menu-modal" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="certifications-title">
    <button class="modal-close" data-close="certifications-modal">×</button>
    <div class="modal-heading">
      <span class="modal-heading-icon certifications-color">◆</span>
      <div><h2 id="certifications-title">Certifications</h2><p>Des bonus conservés après prestige.</p></div>
    </div>
    <div class="prestige-summary">
      <div>
        <span id="prestige-preview-label">PROCHAIN PRESTIGE</span>
        <strong id="prestige-points-preview">0</strong>
      </div>
      <button id="prestige-button" class="danger-button" disabled>RECONSTRUIRE ET PRESTIGER</button>
      <small id="prestige-gain">Prestige disponible à partir de 1 million de requêtes.</small>
      <small id="prestige-capacity">Capacité disponible : 100 %. La saturation commence à 100 millions de requêtes.</small>
    </div>
    <div id="certification-grid" class="certification-grid"></div>
  </section>
</div>

<div class="modal-backdrop" id="missions-modal" aria-hidden="true">
  <section class="modal game-menu-modal missions-modal" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="missions-title">
    <button class="modal-close" data-close="missions-modal">×</button>
    <div class="modal-heading">
      <span class="modal-heading-icon missions-color">✓</span>
      <div><h2 id="missions-title">Missions quotidiennes</h2><p>Trois objectifs renouvelés chaque jour.</p></div>
    </div>
    <div id="missions-grid" class="missions-grid"></div>
    <section class="tomorrow-missions">
      <div class="tomorrow-missions-heading">
        <span>PROCHAIN CYCLE</span>
        <strong id="tomorrow-missions-date">Demain</strong>
      </div>
      <div id="tomorrow-missions-list" class="tomorrow-missions-list"></div>
    </section>
    <p class="missions-reset">Renouvellement à minuit, heure locale.</p>
  </section>
</div>

<div class="modal-backdrop prestige-backdrop" id="prestige-confirm-modal" aria-hidden="true">
  <section class="modal prestige-confirm-modal" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="prestige-confirm-title">
    <button class="modal-close" data-close="prestige-confirm-modal">×</button>
    <div class="prestige-confirm-icon">◆</div>
    <span class="prestige-confirm-kicker">RECONSTRUCTION OPTIONNELLE</span>
    <h2 id="prestige-confirm-title">Convertir cette progression ?</h2>
    <p>Vous pouvez continuer à développer cette infrastructure ou la reconstruire maintenant contre des points de certification.</p>
    <div class="prestige-recap">
      <div><span>Vous gagnez</span><strong id="prestige-confirm-gain">Des points de certification</strong></div>
      <div><span>Réinitialisé</span><strong>Requêtes, bâtiments et améliorations</strong></div>
      <div><span>Conservé</span><strong>Certifications et succès débloqués</strong></div>
    </div>
    <div class="prestige-confirm-actions">
      <button class="secondary-button" data-close="prestige-confirm-modal">Plus tard</button>
      <button id="prestige-confirm-button" class="prestige-confirm-button">Reconstruire maintenant</button>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<div class="modal-backdrop profile-backdrop" id="profile-modal" aria-hidden="true">
  <section class="modal profile-modal" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="profile-title">
    <div class="profile-modal-icon" aria-hidden="true">◎</div>
    <span class="profile-modal-kicker">IDENTITÉ DE L’INFRASTRUCTURE</span>
    <h2 id="profile-title">Choisissez votre pseudo</h2>
    <p>Il sera visible dans le classement public avec le drapeau de votre pays.</p>
    <form id="profile-form">
      <label for="profile-input">Pseudo</label>
      <input id="profile-input" name="username" minlength="3" maxlength="20" autocomplete="nickname" required placeholder="Ex. RootMaster">
      <small>3 à 20 caractères : lettres, chiffres, espaces, tirets ou underscores.</small>
      <p id="profile-error" class="profile-error" role="alert"></p>
      <button type="submit" class="primary-button">Enregistrer mon pseudo</button>
    </form>
  </section>
</div>

<div class="modal-backdrop v2-reset-backdrop" id="v2-reset-modal" aria-hidden="true">
  <section class="modal v2-reset-modal" role="alertdialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="v2-reset-title" aria-describedby="v2-reset-message">
    <div class="v2-reset-icon" aria-hidden="true">↻</div>
    <span class="v2-reset-label">MISE À JOUR V2</span>
    <h2 id="v2-reset-title">Votre progression a été réinitialisée</h2>
    <p id="v2-reset-message">
      Infra Clicker utilise désormais une sauvegarde synchronisée avec le serveur. Une nouvelle partie v2
      vient d’être créée pour utiliser ce format.
    </p>
    <button class="primary-button" data-close="v2-reset-modal">Commencer la v2</button>
  </section>
</div>

<div class="terminal-window" id="terminal-window" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="terminal-titlebar">
    <span><i></i><i></i><i></i></span>
    <strong>root@infra-clicker:~</strong>
    <button id="terminal-close">×</button>
  </div>
  <div class="terminal-output" id="terminal-output">
    <p>InfraOS 1.0.0 — console d'administration</p>
    <p>Tapez <b>help</b> pour afficher les commandes disponibles.</p>
  </div>
  <form id="terminal-form" class="terminal-input-row">
    <label for="terminal-input">root@infra-clicker:~#</label>
    <input id="terminal-input" autocomplete="off" spellcheck="false">
  </form>
</div>
